               <head>Legal texts of Ḥevrat raḥamim in Mantua</head>
               
               
               
               <msContents class="lccn.loc.gov/sh85022662" rend="visible">
                  
                  
                  
                  <summary>Legal texts of Ḥevrat raḥamim in Mantua. </summary>
                  
                  
                  
                  <textLang mainLang="he"/>
                  
                  
                  
                  <msItem rend="">
                     
                     
                     
                     <locus from="1r" to="26v"/>
                     
                     
                     
                     <title xml:lang="he-Latn-x-lc">Pinḳas Ḥevrat raḥamim be-Manṭovah</title>
                     
                     
                     
                     <title xml:lang="he">פנקס חברת רחמים במנטובה</title>
                     
                     
                     
                     <note>
                        
                        
                        
                        <p>The rules of a society called Ḥevrat raḥamim, founded in 1578 in Mantua (folios 1v-14r), with the addition of resolutions subsequently passed by the society (folios 14v-22v). </p>
                        
                        
                        
                        <p>Folios 23r-26r contain a table of contents of the different parts of the manuscript. </p>
                     
                     
                     
                     </note>
                  
                  
                  
                  </msItem>
               
               
               
               </msContents>
               
               
               
